Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.41,0:00:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你这架飞机  弗兰奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I like your plane, Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他自己拼起来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He put it together himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  不过你晚上可得把蔬菜吃光啊  弗兰奇小子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, but you better eat your vegetables tonight, Frankie boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.52,0:00:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子  就一小坏蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That kid. Such a little hooligan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.76,0:00:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像他老子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just like his old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子可是在风暴来之前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You were the one who toilet papered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把邻居家用卫生纸围了个实在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the neighbor's house right before a thunderstorm,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让妈逮了个正着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}until ma busted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼我上门道歉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Marched me over there to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.78,0:00:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一把鼻涕一把泪的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Whining and crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花了你整整一星期才清理完\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Took you, like, a week to clean it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.20,0:00:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,获取部分监护权确实对你有好处  杰西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Getting partial custody's done you good, Jess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.50,0:00:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隔周一周末  每周一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Every other weekend and a day each week.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:51.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗兰奇不用听我和他妈对着吵了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Frankie doesn't have to hear his ma and me hollering at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.31,0:00:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can't complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你戒了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you're dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:57.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三周后就拿到两周年纪念章了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get my two-year chip in...three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.04,0:00:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会来参加吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You coming to the meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.49,0:01:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不错过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Wouldn't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.43,0:01:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你有课或者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If you have class or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:04.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全靠你才读得起法学院\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're the reason I can afford law school anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.66,0:01:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是为了自己有得吹嘘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm just doing it for the bragging rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我弟弟是律师\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My brother the lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:16.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说  你弟弟是检察官\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How about... your brother the prosecutor?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.70,0:01:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才是我真正想要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's what I really wanna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:30.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西・勃兰特\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Jesse Brandt?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局  先生  你得跟我们走一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}FBI, sir. You need to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:34.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们有你的逮捕令\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We have a warrant for your arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.88,0:01:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's okay, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟彼得叔叔待在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You stay with your Uncle Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.52,0:01:42.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罪名是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What are the charges?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.57,0:01:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你们呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I asked you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不必回答  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We don't need to answer your question, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.07,0:01:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国家安全例外  看逮捕令吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}National security exception. Read the warrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥是航空公司的机械师\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My brother's an airline mechanic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.40,0:01:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们抓错人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You got the wrong guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西  不会有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Jesse, it's gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.65,0:02:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会解决的  知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll get this sorted out, okay?
