Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:21.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(245.055,230.6)\K20\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\c&HDBD5CA&\fs10}查找关键执行人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖开口吧  奥托\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You need to talk to us, Otto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All we wanna know is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛的人为什么总是自杀\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why do these Decima guys keep killing themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为保险合同\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's for the insurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人加入组织时都有份保单\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Each agent gets a policy when they join the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦被抓  便一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Get caught, get nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是出了意外\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家属会获得赔偿金\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Their next of kin gets a payday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位赔偿金先生是我们找到芬奇的最后线索了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Payday there was our last lead on Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.45,0:03:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又回到起点了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're back to square one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器说我们还有别的事情需要考虑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The machine says we have other things to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里尔抓了芬奇  他就是我们唯一需要考虑的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Greer has Finch. He's the only thing we have to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.66,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解你的感受  约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I understand how you feel, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.13,0:03:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她确定哈罗德暂时没有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But she assured me Harold's not in immediate danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我们现在还有更大的威胁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And we have a larger threat at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.53,0:03:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要详说下吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You wanna expand on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她看不清全局\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She can't see the full picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器都看不清全局  那要我们如何帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How can we help when the machine can't even see what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.87,0:03:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们当她的耳目\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We'll be her eyes and ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.71,0:03:43.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  招待不周\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I apologize for the... unpleasant accommodation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:48.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于得见一面  实在荣幸  芬奇先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's truly a pleasure to put a face to the name, Mr. Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你已是久仰了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've been wanting to meet you for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要什么  格里尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What is it that you want, Mr. Greer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想谈一下未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I want to talk about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最够资格谈这一话题的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And who more qualified for that conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫过于人工智能之父了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}than the father of artificial intelligence?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利他目标导致的意外副作用罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}An unintended side effect of an altruistic goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利他主义\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Altruism?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还一直以为是出于  创世的权力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd always imagined it was about the power of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.40,0:04:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己感受过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've felt it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你执意将"撒马利亚人"上线\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your endeavor to bring Samaritan online
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是在铸成大错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}is a grave error in judgment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定知道这一刻早晚会到来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You must've known this moment would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是你以为无人可以达到你的成就\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or did you think nobody else could accomplish what you did,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你举世无双\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that you were unique?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.72,0:04:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得承认  你本来把所有人都玩弄于股掌之中了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I must admit you played everyone very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到这一刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}right up until this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.76,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  你的上帝已经失踪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And now your God has disappeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.39,0:04:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行其事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}operating on its own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子有时会让人失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Children can be so disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这世界需要有组织  芬奇先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The world needs structure, Mr. Finch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而"撒马利亚人"可以提供\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and Samaritan will provide that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:58.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心防备伪神  格里尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd beware of false idols, Mr. Greer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.71,0:05:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你若真的确定"撒马利亚人"没问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If you were so confident that Samaritan was functional,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又何必大费周章地找我呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}why did you go to such great lengths to find me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了盯住你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}To keep an eye on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为人工智能之父  你是全世界唯一\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As the father of AI, you're the only man in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.42,0:05:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能毁灭它的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}who can destroy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们现在要如何呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where does that leave us then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.89,0:05:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到"撒马利亚人"睁开它的眼睛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Until the moment Samaritan opens its eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这世界\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And then the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将不再需要你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}will no longer need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.01,0:05:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚是偷了死人的钥匙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Did you just steal a dead man's keys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她要我做的  能借你的刀一用么  约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She asked me to. Can I borrow your knife, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛太狡猾  肯定不会用GPS\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}While Decima's too clever to use GPS...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:06:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星广播带GPS转频器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The satellite radio has a GPS transponder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子们也许能找出点数据\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The boys might be able to pull off some data,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.40,0:06:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查出我们新故的德西玛朋友到过哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}find out where our recently deceased Decima friend has been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:09.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.91,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关上门啊  冻死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Shut the door. It's freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:17.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认识他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I know them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们帮你从科利尔手里救出了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They helped you rescue me from Collier.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那个政府杀手  还逼我拔牙来着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're that government hit man that made me pull out my molars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太野蛮了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放松  凯西  我退休了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Relax, Casey. I'm retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.74,0:06:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在这儿干嘛  根\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What are they doing here, Root?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.15,0:06:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北山  杰森  丹尼尔和我一直在四处收集\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Daizo, Jason, Daniel, and I have been on the road collecting certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:37.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三城区的禁品\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}contraband in the tri-cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着是既含糊又危险啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That sounds both vague and dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能借用下你的安全屋  约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I was hoping we could use your safe house, John,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我们之前救他们可费了不少力气\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}seeing as we went to all the trouble of saving them in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想多跟你情话绵绵一会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And as much as I'd love some girl talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过你得去趟卡尔顿酒店\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you need to go to the Carlton Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要卫星电话干嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And, uh, why do I need a satphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.62,0:06:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我啦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个冬天真是够呛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Quite the winter we're having.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你不是来游说全球气候变化的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't supposed you're here to sell me on global climate change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事先防患于未然\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It would be nice if we could prepare for the future
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.80,0:07:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好过事后找补\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}instead of trying to clean up after the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:17.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天要去见总统的情报顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm meeting with the president's intelligence advisor today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用试运行的成果说服他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Use the beta test results to convince them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"是沉睡的巨人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan is a sleeping giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要用信号来唤醒它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need those feeds to awaken it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.23,0:07:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在努力了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  格里尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't worry, Mr. Greer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们还是想买你的系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They still wanna buy your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"不卖  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan is not for sale, Senator.
