Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会向你们提供关键信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We will provide you the critical information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我向一家私人公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You want me to give a private corporation access
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:45.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供政府信号权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to the government feeds--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提供三亿美国人的隐私权限\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to 300 million Americans--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好让你们把这些信息再卖回给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}just so you can sell the information back to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"比你之前的系统要优秀得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan is far superior to your last endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它能回答你所有的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It'll answer all your questions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不会给谜语猜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It won't create riddles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.34,0:07:59.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有待整理的号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There'll be no numbers to sort through.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有不确定的罪责\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No uncertainties about culpability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有纯粹而不受限制的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just pure unfettered information.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们凭什么同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why would we agree to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我们不能拥有这个系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If we don't own the system,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们还有什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}what exactly do we get?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合理推诿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Plausible deniability.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"属于独立第三方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan is privately owned by a third party,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.30,0:08:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,方便你们下次遇着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}one that can shoulder the blame
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.94,0:08:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公民权益危机时能推卸责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}for your next civil liberties scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.97,0:08:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要是不答应呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And if I say no?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.96,0:08:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的条件已经说了  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Those are my terms, Senator.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得扪心自问\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You must ask yourself this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是想阻止恐怖活动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you wanna prevent acts of terror...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是宁可袖手旁观  坐看国家生灵涂炭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or do you wanna stay in the dark and watch your country burn?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:49.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这些了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's all of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  开始干活吧  小子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Good. Get to work, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿到了"撒马利亚人"七台服务器\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You got your hands on seven Samaritan servers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.79,0:08:56.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在上面有发现吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You find anything on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.10,0:09:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  但稍有差池  他们肯定会发现我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, but they'll definitely find us if we don't get this right.
