Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再想让我闯入满是特勤局特工的房间时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}wants me to break into a room filled with secret service guys
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:49.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预先提醒一下比较好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}a little heads up would be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她知道你能搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She knows you can handle yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  可以监控主控者了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, so we've got eyes and ears on Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟个男人在一起  高个  灰发\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's with some guy-- tall, gray hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.91,0:12:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很严肃啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Very serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.10,0:12:08.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯・加里森参议员  我们的第二个号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Senator Ross Garrison, our second number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们其他朋友到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have their other friends arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.34,0:12:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女人还有朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That woman's got friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.56,0:12:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我帮格里尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You want me to help Greer,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他从我手中偷走了"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the man who stole Samaritan from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.50,0:12:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你的面子先放一边  行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's put your ego aside for a moment, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:22.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗斯  我知道"撒马利亚人"是极好的后备计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ross, I know that Samaritan is an excellent plan "B."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不喜欢花钱买回\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I just don't like having to pay for something
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就属于我的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that belongs to me in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不介意你输掉场战役  只要我们能赢得战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I accept that you lost the battle so we can win the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.07,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  钱不是问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Besides, money isn't the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看过黑色预算  你手上大把钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've seen the black budget. You've got plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.82,0:12:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要的是政府信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What we need are the government feeds,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就需要说服其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and that's going to take some convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没法左右国会的风向  罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't control the way the congressional winds blow, Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那应该是你的地盘\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I really think that's your arena.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国会那边我在处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm handling congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们得说服里维拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But we need Rivera on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统的亲信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The president's bulldog.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:52.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能用你  独特的视角\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I need you to use your... special insight
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说服他这一项目的优势\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to convince him of the program's merits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:58.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们从"撒马利亚人"的试运行中\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There is intel from Samaritan's beta test
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.65,0:13:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现了有用的情报\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that you'll find useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What do I get in return?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个开放的系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}An open system,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为私人企业所有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}one owned by a private entity
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:08.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们得以合理推诿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that gives us plausible deniability
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能继续保护我们的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}while we continue to protect our country
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免受恐怖袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}from terrorist attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做这工作已经数年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've been doing the job for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.97,0:13:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人比你更熟悉游戏规则\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's no one better at this game than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是游戏  而是国家安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is not a game, this is national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.10,0:13:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如让我看看这情报吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why don't you let me see the intel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are you two hearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们要跟德西玛勾搭  实行《一九八四》式威权监控\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They're ready to get in bed with Decima and go all 1984 on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}典故出自奥威尔经典政治讽刺小说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.82,0:13:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  比现在还狠的  我把他们全突突得了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I mean...more than usual. Let me just shoot 'em now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还不知道他们是不是行凶者  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We still don't know if they're the perpetrators yet, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.33,0:13:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.39,0:13:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是主控者  她差点杀了你  根\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's Control. She almost killed you, Root,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.06,0:13:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我  还有哈罗德  还要列举吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and me and Harold. Should I continue?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.58,0:13:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人孰无过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We all make mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看正门  看到什么  \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Look at the front door. What do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:03.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多政府车牌\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}More government plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-都是号码  -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- These our other numbers? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国安局的头  卡尔・霍尔库姆将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Head of the NSA, General Kyle Holcombe,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.01,0:14:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有曼纽・里维拉  总统高级顾问\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and Manuel Rivera, senior advisor to the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那第五个号码呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And what about the fifth number?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是个问号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That one's still a question mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:17.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  就确认一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, so... just to confirm,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是说我还不能杀主控者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you're saying I can't kill Control yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.28,0:14:22.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚持住啊  萨姆恩\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Stay the course, Sameen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头要失控了  别怪我没提醒过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But just remember I told you so when all this goes pear-shaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.55,0:14:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备找点乐子了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You ready to have some fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就怕你不问呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I thought you'd never ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.62,0:14:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有见过初生的小马\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Have you ever seen a newborn foal
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.56,0:14:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次想站起来的样子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}trying to stand for the first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战栗着腿  努力想保持平衡\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Those trembling legs trying to balance,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四条腿一直在抖动  直到它终于能站稳\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Shaking until the moment it finds itself on all fours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.06,0:15:02.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见证孩子踏出的第一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Seeing a child walk for the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在是美妙\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}is something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你眼看着自己的孩子站了起来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But you watched your child stand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.42,0:15:12.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却又废了它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and then you hobbled it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.35,0:15:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不会明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You could never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.68,0:15:18.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是毁灭者  而非创造者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're a destroyer, not a creator.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.48,0:15:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说下去  芬奇先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm listening, Mr. Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.53,0:15:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的机器...\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发展出了我未预料到的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}it started developing abilities I never expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.51,0:15:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有编程过的能力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}things I hadn't yet programmed it to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时世上已没有任何算法\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And there wasn't an algorithm in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.93,0:15:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能控制它的急速成长\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that could control its exponential growth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到我自己写出来时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And by the time I figured one out myself
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怕是太迟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}it would've been too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么太迟了  -这还不是问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Too late for what? - Isn't that just the question?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的创造  比我自身聪明太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Having built something significantly smarter than myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如何能预测出其进化\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}how could I possibly anticipate its evolution?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不确定性  你的无间地狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Uncertainty. Your personal abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:15:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我造机器是要拯救生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I built the machine to save lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:01.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我如何确保机器不会在某天\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but how could I be certain that it wouldn't one day
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为全人类都是无关号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}determine that all of humanity was irrelevant?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  不要激活"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Please, you cannot allow Samaritan to go online.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个开放系统所带来的后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the consequences of an open system
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会是灾难性的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}will be devastating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲惧怕儿子的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The father became fearful of his son,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是伤害他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}so he wounded him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同样的故事总是一再发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A tale told time and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}希腊神话中的泰坦与宙斯  详见S02E13
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不把"撒马利亚人"视为孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I don't think of Samaritan as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没那么狂妄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm not that presumptuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.79,0:16:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要让它尽显才华\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I plan to celebrate its brilliance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.17,0:16:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而非限制它\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}not muzzle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自以为能控制如此强大的力量  太过自负\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's pure hubris to think that you can control something so powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁说我要控制它了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Whoever said I wanted to control it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来是当你朋友  罗斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm only here because we're friends, Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.06,0:16:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统说得很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The president has made it very clear
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.32,0:17:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会再冒险实施其他监控项目了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}he will not risk his hide on another surveillance program.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Neither will I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:04.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里维拉先生  我能否\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Rivera, if I may--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当然能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You certainly may.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:07.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直负责运行这项目\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You've been the one running this program.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.87,0:17:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也该解释解释了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's high time you explained yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.88,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我花了多长时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you know how many hours I've spent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为"北极光"擦屁股打掩护\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}running interference for this Northern Lights debacle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的公民权益组织  从纽约到香港\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Every civil liberties group from New York to Hong Kong
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.92,0:17:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全在为这倒霉东西发疯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}has their panties in a twist over this damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.04,0:17:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然很不幸  但我们还是得保护国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}As unfortunate as that is, we still need to protect our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要我去请求自由世界的领导者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You want me to ask the leader of the free world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,批准又一个国民监控项目吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to approve another domestic surveillance program,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而此时民众还刚开始获知\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}when people are still learning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.80,0:17:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前一个见不得人的秘密\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the dirty little secrets of the old one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没戏\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm not biting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:38.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里维拉先生  你有孩子对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Rivera, you have kids, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.51,0:17:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么意思  -他们上国家中学\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Your point? - They go to Country Day School.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.34,0:17:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Again, your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很棒的学校  一流\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's a terrific school, top notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在乔治敦27街和0街交界处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's in Georgetown near 27th and "0" street.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我告诉你  一年前\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What if I told you that, a year ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北极光阻止了一起针对乔治敦的恐怖袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Northern Lights prevented a terrorist attack in Georgetown?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的一名特工拦截并处死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}An operator of ours intercepted and executed
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那名恐怖分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that would-be terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她发现他在一辆未登记的厢式客车里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She found him sitting in an unmarked sedan
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一枚放射性炸弹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}with a radiological bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用从牙科X光机里偷来的铯自己做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was made from the cesium that he stole from a dental X-ray machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这是编故事逼我就范\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're making up ghost stories to force my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-要有这种事我会知情  -不  你不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- I would've heard about this. - No, you wouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.87,0:18:19.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会每次救完人就发新闻稿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We don't send out a press release every time we save lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.52,0:18:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当公众站在房顶高喊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And while the public shouts from the rooftops
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公民权益时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}about their civil liberties...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.46,0:18:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护他们的  正是他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}they do so under the protective bubble
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.58,0:18:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所竭力反对的项目\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of the very program in which they're railing against,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这项目保护他们免遭恐怖袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the one that saves them from terrorist attacks
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.28,0:18:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时时刻刻\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}every single day,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.12,0:18:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括国际的  国内的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}International and domestic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"  我听过相关汇报\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Vigilance. I was briefed on this group.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们尚不知他们下个目标是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We don't know who they're targeting next,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.62,0:18:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但该组织从不小打小闹\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but this group never does anything small.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来24小时内他们将发动袭击\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They're set to strike in the next 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一能阻止这次袭击的法子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The only way that we can stop this attack
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是再次授权政府信号\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}is for us to get the government feeds back up
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让"撒马利亚人"能尽职工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and allow Samaritan to do its job.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了  要是你打算\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Unless of course you want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视而不见\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}ignore the facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.82,0:19:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等国丧时再去负责清理残骸吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and you can handle the cleanup duty once there's a national tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会仔细看的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll read through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.91,0:19:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你慢慢来\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Take your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惜我赶时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Unfortunately I've just run out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得横穿市区开个会去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I've got a meeting across town.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回头再找你  曼纽\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'll check in with you later, Manuel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.45,0:19:36.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主控者刚才全场紧逼\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Control just went in for the full-court press
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备统治世界了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}on total world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.87,0:19:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能杀她了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Can I kill her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.20,0:19:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你们要卖什么  我都没兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Listen, whatever you're selling I'm not interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.14,0:19:54.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不是卖东西的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He's not selling anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是有几个问题想问你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We just have a few questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:23.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好别动  会加快失血\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Probably shouldn't move. It'll bleed more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尼尔・雅各布斯  纽约驾照\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Niall Jacobs, New York license.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么重要的呢  尼尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why are you important, Niall?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.00,0:20:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦走狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Fed pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是慢半拍\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Always ten steps behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不是政府的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Guess he's not government.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.31,0:20:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\c&HE6E1C7&\fs9\frz11.79\move(70.874,69.056,64.067,51.39,1775,2860)}验证中  病毒验证\N{\K170\fs1}\h\N{\K85\fs9}震网病毒变体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.51,0:20:53.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.52,0:20:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,震网改进病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A Stuxnet-based virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位创意天才做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What did this creative genius make?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.38,0:21:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像是自我复制型的蠕虫病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Looks like a self-replicating worm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.64,0:21:02.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用来攻击什么系统\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Designed to attack what kind of system?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,专用微型交换机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A proprietary micro-switcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.05,0:21:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但具体针对什么  她也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But for what... she doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器精良\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Expensive hardware...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐蔽得力\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Hiding in plain sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.41,0:21:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,训练有素\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Well trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.55,0:21:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是"时刻警惕"的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're Vigilance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚是说"时刻警惕"吗  因为\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Did you say "Vigilance?" because...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.19,0:21:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是来干掉主控者和其他人的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It must be to kill Control and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.66,0:21:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太喜欢落井下石\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm not a big fan of kicking a guy when he's down,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.12,0:21:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管用啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}sometimes it does the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说出你们的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now tell us your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道我的部分\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I only know my part.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:43.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们会赢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's why we're going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们聪明过你们和你们的法西斯朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're smarter than you and your fascist friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来不及阻止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're too late to stop it from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Stop what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,革命\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The revolution.
