Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.41,0:22:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么花了这么久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why is it taking so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.79,0:22:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经两周了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It has been two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:17.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥在接受联邦调查  勃兰特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your brother's under federal investigation, Mr. Brandt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们没有起诉他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They haven't charged him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.95,0:22:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至不允许他接受审讯时有律师在场\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}they haven't even allowed him to speak with an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.63,0:22:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们违反了所有法律程序\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You are breaking every rule that ensures due process,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我扯什么"国家安全例外"的废话\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and do not give me that national security exception crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.72,0:22:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我都清楚那条法律是应对紧迫威胁的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You and I both know that law was intended for immediate threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.17,0:22:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西很可能就是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Jesse very well may be one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.40,0:22:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥这一生从没违反过一条法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My brother's never broken a law in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.46,0:22:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他每周工作六十个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He works 60 hours a week,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按时付房租  他是个好父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}he pays his rent on time, he's a good father.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.08,0:22:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你说  你们抓错人了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm telling you you got the wrong guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个聪明人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're a bright guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,显然你深爱你哥哥\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you obviously love your brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常爱  我尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}very much. I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.45,0:22:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有时候我们至爱之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But sometimes the people we love the most
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:23:00.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会误入歧途\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}make the worst decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.31,0:23:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西和一个叫阿齐兹・易卜拉欣的人有联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Jesse has connections to a man named Aziz Al-ibrahim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,易卜拉欣的表亲\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Al-ibrahim's cousin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.01,0:23:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伊斯兰恐怖组织的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}was part of an Islamist terrorist group
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.45,0:23:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在3月11号试图炸毁美国驻埃及大使馆\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that tried to blow up an American embassy in Egypt on March 11th.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是张照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This is just a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我再补充几张\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then let me add to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.63,0:23:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们甚至不是穆斯林\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're not even Muslim.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.06,0:23:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这根本说不通啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I mean, this doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两年你哥哥的生活发生了一些变化\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Two years ago your brother made some changes in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.29,0:23:33.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直在酗酒  他妻子离开了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He'd been drinking, his wife left him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.33,0:23:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但之后  杰西的人生改变了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But then, Jesse turned his life around.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.26,0:23:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候当我们陷入低谷时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sometimes when we hit bottom...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会求助于错误的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we ask the wrong people for help--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.74,0:23:45.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人会利用我们的软弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}people who use our weaknesses against us,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驱使我们做一些  我们本以为自己永远不能做\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}get us to do things that we never thought we could,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会做的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or would.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.28,0:23:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不可能是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}this can't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.91,0:23:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监视不会说谎  勃兰特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Surveillance doesn't lie, Mr. Brandt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.71,0:24:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我们要对战"时刻警惕"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If we're going up against Vigilance,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.09,0:24:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要更多的弹药\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we're gonna need more ammo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.08,0:24:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莱奈尔抓走咖啡店那位之前  我从他身上顺了些\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I took some from our coffee shop friend before Lionel picked him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.52,0:24:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弹药应该足以撑到下一站\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We should be okay until our next stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.69,0:24:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好极了  又有活儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Terrific. More errands.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要对抗两个隐形的敌人  约翰\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're fighting two invisible enemies, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:21.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛和"时刻警惕"都知道机器的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima and Vigilance know about the machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.45,0:24:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们很聪明  能绕过她行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}These groups are clever, blinding her to their actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.31,0:24:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就叫你的智囊团快搞定\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then get that brain trust of yours on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.51,0:24:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我受够了机器的搪塞\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm getting tired of the machine's runaround
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.13,0:24:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇还在别人手里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}when Finch is still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.42,0:24:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.49,0:24:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我进度\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Gimme a timetable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.29,0:24:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她问我们预计时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's asking for an ETA.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.90,0:24:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们碰到了一些硬件问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, we've run into a couple of kinks with the hardware.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须更新所有设备\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We've had to retrofit everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.02,0:24:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要多少时间  丹尼尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How much time, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.81,0:24:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起码两小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}At least two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地理定位数据怎么样了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What about the geo-locator data?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.46,0:24:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,北山正在弄\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Daizo's still working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.34,0:24:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想告诉我接下来去哪儿  好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You don't wanna tell me where we're going, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.43,0:25:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我要知道你的粉丝团在干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But I wanna know what those groupies of yours are working on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.27,0:25:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拖延我们的敌人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Something to slow down our enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.60,0:25:12.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿到我们要的东西了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Do you have what we need?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.88,0:25:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早拿到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Got it this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.66,0:25:18.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Shaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.59,0:25:21.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看你可以去跟旧老板聊聊天了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think it's time you had a chat with your old boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.15,0:25:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.06,0:25:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得聊聊我如何宰了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We'll chat about how I'm gonna kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.96,0:25:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君子动口不动手\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Use your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.63,0:25:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  她这次是受害者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, so she's the victim this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.28,0:25:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那下次呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But what about the next?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.60,0:25:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Listen, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.52,0:25:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然主控者跟格里尔有联系\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If Control's in touch with Greer,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.03,0:25:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就能带着我们找到哈罗德\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}she'll lead us to Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.73,0:25:34.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是一时手痒没忍住  \N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your trigger finger gets itchy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.91,0:25:36.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们落了空  他会死\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}we'll get nothing and he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.24,0:25:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阴啊  里瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Low blow, Reese.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.61,0:25:57.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-肖探员  -夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- Agent Shaw. - Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.47,0:26:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久没用枪指着你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Long time no gunfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.10,0:26:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你认识这女人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know this woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.21,0:26:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得在你孩子的学校附近处理了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You remember the operator who took out the terrorist
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.61,0:26:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖份子的特工吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}near your children's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.32,0:26:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.46,0:26:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不敢相信我居然要说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can't believe what I'm about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.86,0:26:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来救你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm here to rescue you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.59,0:26:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Root.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.30,0:26:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么新消息吗  杰森\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You have an update for me, Jason?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.91,0:26:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰森和我梳理了病毒的代码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Jason and I combed through the virus's code.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.00,0:26:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的攻击目标是定制的微型交换机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's targeting custom-built micro-switchers
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.62,0:26:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一家公司采购过\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}sold to one company.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.63,0:26:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪一家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.52,0:26:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电力公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The power company.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.61,0:26:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去帮肖  快\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Help Shaw. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.16,0:26:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.88,0:26:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}All of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.65,0:26:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收到了我们的号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You received our numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.03,0:26:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有加里森的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Garrison's too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.67,0:26:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始还以为你是行凶者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thought you were the perp at first since, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.16,0:26:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可害了不少人  夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}you've stung a lotta frogs, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.34,0:26:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要保护我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why are you protecting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.71,0:26:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这是  计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}'Cause that's part of the... plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.31,0:26:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了什么大局之类的着想\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}For the greater good, or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.74,0:26:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Look, honestly, I really don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.66,0:26:52.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道马上要出事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I just know something bad's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.91,0:26:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肖  我马上过去\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Shaw, I'm heading your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.84,0:27:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里瑟  这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Reese? What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.02,0:27:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是说马上要出事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know that bad thing that was gonna happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.00,0:27:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在出了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think it just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.09,0:27:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How's he holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.93,0:27:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不肯谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He won't talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.81,0:27:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.21,0:27:36.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西本来挺好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Jesse had been doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.65,0:27:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.96,0:27:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那次逮捕打垮了他  彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That arrest did him in, Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.87,0:27:42.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们怎么能随便把人扔进监狱\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How do they just put someone in jail like that
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.64,0:27:44.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都不说\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and not tell you anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.95,0:27:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是他出来后我没有争取完整监护权\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Maybe if I hadn't taken full custody after they let him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.59,0:27:50.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他酗酒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He was drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.74,0:27:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在保护你的儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You were protecting your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.62,0:27:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西自杀不是你的错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's not your fault Jesse killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.38,0:28:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都要对自己的行为负责\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're all responsible for our own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.90,0:28:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去陪陪弗兰奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm go sit with Frankie.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.74,0:28:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想打扰你们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I didn't mean to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.49,0:28:14.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只想来说一句\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I just wanted to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.61,0:28:16.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请节哀顺变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}how terribly sorry I am for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.29,0:28:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.64,0:28:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西和我是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Jesse and I were friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.02,0:28:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.15,0:28:22.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我怎么不认识你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then why don't I know you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.72,0:28:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是我的担保人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He was my sponsor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.17,0:28:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是杰西  我早就死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'd be dead if it wasn't for Jesse.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.08,0:28:41.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他挽救了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He saved my life in so many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.08,0:28:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望我当时有帮他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I wish I had been there for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.04,0:28:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.92,0:28:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个远房亲戚害我全家惹上了麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A distant relative caused problems for my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.05,0:28:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们几乎不认识他  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We barely knew him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.91,0:28:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在都无关紧要了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that doesn't matter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.37,0:29:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥是我所认识的最正派的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your brother was the most decent man I've ever known.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.52,0:29:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个送你  我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's for you, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.53,0:29:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不能接受  -这样你会记得\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- I can't. - So you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.55,0:29:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你哥哥杀了自己\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that even though your brother killed himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.40,0:29:21.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他拯救过别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}he saved someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.21,0:29:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一系列的停电事故\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A series of power failures...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.75,0:29:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\c&H0B00CE&\fs8\move(199.007,227.4,199.007,214,0,360)}停电事故\N{\fs1}\h\N{\fs6.7\c&H060606&}纽约五区
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.09,0:29:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(146.553,245.71)\K30\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\c&HE8EADA&\fs8\t(2731,2732,\c&H8B8A7B&)}获取替换信号{\K247}\h{\K20\c&HE8EADA&}手机信号塔备用电力
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.61,0:29:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约电网预计至少要48小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The NY DWT has estimated at least 48 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.18,0:29:45.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成千上万的人在想方设法回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Thousands of people trying to make their way home...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.24,0:30:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(197.806,130.617,197.406,146.677)\bord0\shad0\fn方正兰亭粗黑_GBK\c&HAC7D24&\fs10\frx2\fry0\frz61.27}服务出错\N\N失去信号
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.14,0:30:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还暖和吗  芬奇先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are you warm enough, Mr. Finch?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.82,0:30:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.44,0:30:18.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停电时我总会想起我的童年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I always think of my youth when the power goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.05,0:30:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时停电是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Blackouts were a...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.00,0:30:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家常便饭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}everyday occurrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.18,0:30:26.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伦敦大轰炸\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The Blitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.44,0:30:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德军的空袭持续了九个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}German air raids lasted nine months.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.77,0:30:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉好像几年\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Felt like years.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.69,0:30:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时一定很小\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You must've been very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.99,0:30:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,母亲和我经常睡在地铁隧道里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My mother and I used to sleep in the tube
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.99,0:30:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟其他许多家庭一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}along with many other families.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.30,0:30:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一晚我们去地铁站迟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}One night we were late getting to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.93,0:30:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我数月来头一次看到夕阳\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And I saw the sunset for the first time in...months.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.86,0:30:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我有生以来见过的最美风景\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was the most beautiful thing I'd ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.05,0:30:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那其实并非夕阳\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But it wasn't a sunset at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.42,0:31:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是天空在燃烧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The sky was on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.75,0:31:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你后来参军了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Is that why you joined the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.11,0:31:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计是  鉴于我对你的了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}A high probability, given what I've learned about you
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.78,0:31:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及你对国家安全的兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and your interest in national security.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.90,0:31:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我成人后\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}By the time I was an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.91,0:31:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争已不再那么直接\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}wars were no longer quite so straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.89,0:31:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你加入了军情六处\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You were MI6.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,民族国家的时代已经结束了  芬奇先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The era of the nation-state is over, Mr. Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.76,0:31:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边界已不复存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There are no more borders.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.67,0:31:34.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没注意到吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or hadn't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.38,0:31:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得你高估了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think you're overestimating
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.75,0:31:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人工智能的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the power of artificial intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.25,0:31:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你我都清楚事实并非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We both know that that is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.48,0:31:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争中  同盟经常会打乱重组\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How often alliances shift in times of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.37,0:31:55.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些同盟其实  并不存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not that those alliances...ever truly exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.45,0:31:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是假象\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They're an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.60,0:32:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同天空燃烧时  错觉的夕阳\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Like seeing a sunset in a sky of flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.52,0:32:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想通过"撒马利亚人"得到什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What is it you expect from Samaritan?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.53,0:32:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想生活在公正的世界里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I want to live under a more just rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.31,0:32:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"撒马利亚人"永远不会和秘书上床\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Samaritan will never sleep with its secretary,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.69,0:32:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是贪污挪用竞选经费\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}or embezzle money from its campaign fund.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.97,0:32:26.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的决策只基于纯粹的逻辑\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Its decisions will be based on pure logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.78,0:32:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这  才是我们该推举的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now...that's a leader deserving of our vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.51,0:32:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  谁带枪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, who's strapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.49,0:32:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.35,0:32:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本以为今天有保镖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I thought my protection detail
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.79,0:32:49.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就火力足够了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}would be all the fire power I needed today.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.07,0:32:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  那你跟在我后边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay. Well, then you're behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.11,0:32:54.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你里维拉  你在右翼  将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You too, Rivera. Flank right, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.48,0:32:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.78,0:33:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在我们后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They're behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.74,0:33:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将军\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}General!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.54,0:33:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.98,0:33:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下来了  开动发电机\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm coming down. Start the generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.49,0:33:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解决她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.73,0:33:57.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉来晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.56,0:34:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我看你来得正是时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, as far as I'm concerned you were right on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.66,0:34:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's Root?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.89,0:34:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灯全灭了算怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And what the hell happened with the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.56,0:34:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"向电网上传了病毒\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Vigilance uploaded a virus into the power grid.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.33,0:34:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主控者呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's Control?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.33,0:34:11.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科利尔抓走了她和里维拉\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Collier got her and Rivera.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.29,0:34:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他们还活着\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But he took 'em alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.89,0:34:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"还有其它计划\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Vigilance has something else planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.78,0:34:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但是什么呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, but what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.54,0:34:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子们搞定服务器了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Are the boys finished with the servers yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.81,0:34:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们快到了  -几分钟就好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- We're almost there. - Minutes away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.34,0:34:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉来挤一下\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I just had to ride up here for a bit.
