Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.29,0:34:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.57,0:34:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你朋友说什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}What'd your friend say?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.50,0:34:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得警告他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I have to warn them.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.81,0:34:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你不会愿意相信我  赫什\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're not gonna believe me, Hersh.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.04,0:35:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们不是来杀主控者的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But we're not here to kill Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.28,0:35:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是来救她的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're here to save her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.85,0:35:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撒谎也要有点水平  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You can lie better than that, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.69,0:35:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们停止接受号码\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Just 'cause you stopped listening to the numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.25,0:35:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不代表号码就不跳了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Doesn't mean they've stopped coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.78,0:35:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么"时刻警惕"不直接杀了他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why didn't Vigilance just kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.72,0:35:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That's a good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.31,0:35:25.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在真不是时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now's not a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.11,0:35:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得我说过芬奇暂时没有危险吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Remember when I said Finch wasn't in imminent danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.67,0:35:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能过于轻率了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I may have been a little hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.47,0:35:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}In good news...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.77,0:35:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道第五个号码是谁了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I know who the fifth number belongs to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.49,0:35:38.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它被好几个假名掩盖了  但是\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It was tucked away under several aliases, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.80,0:35:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,军情六处也瞒不了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}even MI6 can't hide from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.92,0:35:43.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Greer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.06,0:35:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里尔抓了芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And Greer has Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.65,0:35:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说"时刻警惕"快抓到他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Which means that Vigilance is about to have him
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.82,0:35:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非我们抢先一步\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}unless we can get to him first.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.85,0:35:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来不及赶到那里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You won't make it there in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.45,0:35:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"那里"是哪里  根\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's "there," Root?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.41,0:35:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚不清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Still too hard to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.03,0:35:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们怎么找他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then how are we supposed to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.97,0:35:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器也不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The machine doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.15,0:36:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但赫什知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}But Hersh does.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.85,0:36:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万小心  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Be careful, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.77,0:36:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芬奇在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Where's Finch?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.09,0:36:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得我知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You think I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.15,0:36:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朋友从不出错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My friend is never wrong,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.50,0:36:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个  听着都烦人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}which is... as annoying as that sounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.83,0:36:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德西玛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Decima.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.27,0:36:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道哪儿能找到他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know where to find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.50,0:36:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我凭什么要相信你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Why would I trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.74,0:36:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没朝你开枪  你可是要杀我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I haven't shot you yet and you did try to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.57,0:36:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他确实杀了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He did kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.73,0:36:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奉命行事罢了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Those were my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.06,0:36:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说你也报复了  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Besides, you got me back, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.50,0:36:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差得远呢  我只给你下了药\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Oh, not even close. I drugged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.27,0:36:29.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可是还有心跳呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I left you with your heart still beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.00,0:36:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像跑题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I think we're getting off topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.77,0:36:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.69,0:36:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须合作  救出芬奇\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need to work together to save Finch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.90,0:36:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出我们的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We save our friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.11,0:36:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就帮你救主控者\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}then we help you rescue Control.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.02,0:36:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里瑟\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Reese.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.23,0:36:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}It's the right move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.54,0:36:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该你了  肖\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Your turn, Shaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.81,0:36:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想  乔治\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Not on your life, George.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.93,0:37:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这简直是万无一失嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}There's no way this could go wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.50,0:37:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来晚了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.69,0:37:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你试试在断电时横穿市区\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You try getting across town in a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.62,0:37:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.86,0:37:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全世界最重要的人  参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That is the most important man in the world, Senator,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.31,0:37:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新纪元之父\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the father of the new age.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.59,0:37:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手下传来消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My team just got word
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.69,0:37:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"时刻警惕"绑架了我的同僚\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that Vigilance kidnapped my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.89,0:37:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们得尽快出城\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We need to get out of the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.85,0:37:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕我们没有时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm afraid we won't have enough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.40,0:37:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加里森参议员\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Senator Garrison.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.72,0:37:33.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.84,0:37:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的人真该加密一下短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}your men should really encrypt their text messages.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.74,0:37:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者干脆别发短信\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Or avoid them altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.55,0:37:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绑架参议员够你判无期的\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Kidnapping a senator will get you life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.57,0:37:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,格里尔先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Mr. Greer.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.74,0:37:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Pleasure to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.00,0:37:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我通常不太喜欢惊喜\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm not usually a fan of surprises,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.87,0:37:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这次\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but this...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.75,0:38:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我倒是乐于接受\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}this is one I'll happily except.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.22,0:38:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈罗德  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Harold, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.55,0:38:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们上次的谈话被仓促打断了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You know, our last conversation was so rudely interrupted
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.48,0:38:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有一堆问题要问你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and I still have so many questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.23,0:38:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我们一起走\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.97,0:38:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰登呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}So where is Langdon?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.09,0:38:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他去华盛顿特区工作了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He took a job in D.C.,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.81,0:38:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我很了解你哥哥的案子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}but I'm familiar with your brother's case.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.05,0:38:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们认为和他同伙的那个人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}The man you thought he was working with
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.54,0:38:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实只是匿名戒酒会的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}turned out to be just a friend from AA.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.67,0:38:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥不是恐怖分子\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My brother wasn't a terrorist.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.99,0:38:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了你哥哥的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I heard what happened with your brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.00,0:38:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请节哀顺变\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}and I am terribly sorry for your loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.82,0:38:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我扯这些陈词滥调了  行吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Don't give me your platitudes, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.26,0:38:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们逼得他自杀了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You people are the reason he killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.36,0:38:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我们有证据  -你们有个屁\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- We had evidence... - You had nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.19,0:38:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们肆意关押他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You locked him up under some loophole
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.88,0:38:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到毁了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}until it destroyed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.75,0:38:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他失去了工作  失去了家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He lost his job, he lost his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.07,0:39:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影射产生的谣言  伤害程度如同定罪\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Innuendo turned out to be just as damaging as a conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.60,0:39:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他永远都洗不清\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}He could never be cleared...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.77,0:39:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为政府从没有提出控告\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}because the government never pressed charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.34,0:39:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无辜之人不会自杀  勃兰特先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Innocent people don't kill themselves, Mr. Brandt.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.20,0:39:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会  失去希望的人会\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}No, people without hope do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.48,0:39:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们夺去了他的希望\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you robbed him of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.91,0:39:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们拿着错误的信息  加以屈解\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You took the wrong information and you twisted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.24,0:39:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们应该关押罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're supposed to lock up the criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.35,0:39:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而非制造罪犯\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}not create them.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.73,0:39:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们夺去了我哥哥的生命  那你们算什么人\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And you took my brother's life, so what does that make you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.50,0:40:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\move(150.957,196.461,168.976,200.208)\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HF9F6E0&\fs11\b1\frz348.9}短信\N未知\N{\b0}我知道你有问题\N我有答案
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.46,0:40:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\move(160.957,196.461,160,200.208)\bord0\shad0\fn微软雅黑\c&HE2D9A1&\fs11\b1\frz341.3}短信\N未知\N{\b0}你想知道你哥哥真正的遭遇吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.86,0:40:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的车在外边\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}My car's out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.06,0:40:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还想开车吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You think you're driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.37,0:40:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你别想开\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}You're certainly not driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.97,0:40:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我来开  -我心领了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}- I'll drive. - I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.80,0:40:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  这么办\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Okay, here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.19,0:40:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来开车  里瑟坐在后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I'm gonna drive, Reese sits in the back,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.64,0:40:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你坐副驾  同意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}while you ride shotgun, agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.35,0:40:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了  服务器好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}We're done. The servers are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.75,0:40:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间正好\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.63,0:40:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们只能到这里了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Because this is as far as you boys go.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.15,0:41:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所需的一切都在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Everything you need is inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.54,0:41:04.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那辆车会送你们每个人去该去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That car'll take each of you where you need to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.82,0:41:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(190,239)\fs15\bord0}等等
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.94,0:41:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(190,240)\fs15\bord0}你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.50,0:41:12.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经经历了那么多  不会现在丢下你\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Yeah, we've come this far. We're not leaving you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.34,0:41:13.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已经计算过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}She's done the math.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.87,0:41:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去的话  你们全都会死  我也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If we go together, you all die and... I do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.47,0:41:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我独自前往  胜率会好点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}If I go alone, the odds improve.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.11,0:41:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好一点点\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.56,0:41:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你到底要去哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And just where are you going exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.87,0:41:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小子们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.02,0:41:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,见见"撒马利亚人"\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}meet Samaritan.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.62,0:41:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们不在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}They're not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.24,0:41:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那他们在哪儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Then where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.59,0:42:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法表达  这一刻我等了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}I can't tell you how long I've waited for this moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.30,0:42:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们大家等了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}How long we've all been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.25,0:42:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就要将真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now is the time to expose the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.95,0:42:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公布于众\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}to our fellow citizens...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.38,0:42:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真相已经被隐藏太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}the truth that has been lurking beneath the shadows for so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.98,0:42:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以至于国已非国\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}that their country is no longer theirs...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.88,0:42:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由已被剥夺\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}That their freedoms have been stripped away...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.79,0:42:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一台摄像机  一部手机  一兆字节  一点一滴\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}one camera, one cell phone, one megabyte at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.96,0:42:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在该拉开帷幕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Now's the time to pull back the curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.55,0:42:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到你们的审判  女士们先生们\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Welcome to your trial, ladies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.19,0:42:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎来到\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}And welcome to the trial...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.41,0:42:55.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对美国政府的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}of the United States government.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.74,0:43:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\b0\fs14\3c&H000000&\shad1}Court is now in session.


